<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="description" content="A complete record of every tax and fee increase enacted under Governor Mills since 2019. 32 increases. No spin.">
<title>32 Times: Maine Tax Tracker | Lead Maine</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;700;800;900&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg:        #FFFFFF;
  --bg2:       #F7F7F5;
  --bg3:       #EEECEA;
  --text:      #1A1A1A;
  --muted:     #6B7280;
  --border:    #E2E0DC;
  --red:       #C8281F;
  --gold:      #9A6F1A;
  --cat-consumer: #B45309;
  --cat-income:   #B91C1C;
  --cat-payroll:  #7C3AED;
  --cat-business: #1D4ED8;
  --cat-healthcare:#0F766E;
  --cat-fee:      #4F46E5;
  --cat-fiscal:   #374151;
  --radius:    5px;
  --mono: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  --serif: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
  --cond: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
}
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
#tracker, #sources { scroll-margin-top: calc(var(--thead-top, 104px) + 1rem); }
body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
a { color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; }
a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

/* ===== MASTHEAD ===== */
.masthead {
  background: #FFFFFF;
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--red);
  box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
}
.masthead-inner {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 1.5rem;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 2rem;
  height: 56px;
}
.masthead-brand {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 0.75rem;
}
.masthead-count {
  font-family: var(--cond);
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  line-height: 1;
  color: var(--red);
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}
.masthead-title {
  font-family: var(--cond);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.2;
}
.masthead-title span { color: var(--muted); display: block; font-weight: 400; }
.masthead-stats {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0;
  align-items: center;
  justify-self: end;
}
.mstat {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 0 1.25rem;
}
.mstat-val {
  font-family: var(--cond);
  font-weight: 800;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  line-height: 1;
  color: var(--red);
}
.mstat-label {
  font-family: var(--cond);
  font-size: 0.6rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.masthead-nav {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  font-family: var(--cond);
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.masthead-nav a { color: var(--muted); transition: color 0.2s; }
.masthead-nav a:hover { color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }

/* ===== FILTER BAR ===== */
.filter-bar {
  background: var(--bg2);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  position: sticky;
  top: var(--masthead-h, 62px);
  z-index: 50;
}
.filter-bar-inner {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0.55rem 1.5rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}
.cat-chips { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.35rem; }
.cat-chip {
  font-family: var(--cond);
  font-size: 0.73rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
  border-radius: 20px;
  cursor: pointer;
  border: 1px solid transparent;
  transition: all 0.12s;
  user-select: none;
  line-height: 1.4;
}
.cat-chip.active { color: #fff; }
.cat-chip:not(.active) { background: #fff; color: var(--muted); border-color: var(--border); }
.cat-chip:not(.active):hover { color: var(--text); border-color: #aaa; }
.cat-chip[data-cat="all"].active      { background: var(--red); border-color: var(--red); }
.cat-chip[data-cat="consumer"].active  { background: var(--cat-consumer); border-color: var(--cat-consumer); }
.cat-chip[data-cat="income"].active    { background: var(--cat-income); border-color: var(--cat-income); }
.cat-chip[data-cat="payroll"].active   { background: var(--cat-payroll); border-color: var(--cat-payroll); }
.cat-chip[data-cat="business"].active  { background: var(--cat-business); border-color: var(--cat-business); }
.cat-chip[data-cat="healthcare"].active{ background: var(--cat-healthcare); border-color: var(--cat-healthcare); }
.cat-chip[data-cat="fee"].active       { background: var(--cat-fee); border-color: var(--cat-fee); }
.cat-chip[data-cat="fiscal"].active    { background: var(--cat-fiscal); border-color: var(--cat-fiscal); }
.filter-count {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  color: var(--muted);
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.filter-count span { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }

/* ===== TABLE ===== */
.table-wrap {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 1.5rem 2rem;
}
table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.875rem; }
thead th {
  font-family: var(--cond);
  font-size: 0.67rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
  padding: 0.65rem 0.75rem;
  text-align: left;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  background: var(--bg);
  position: sticky;
  top: var(--thead-top, 104px);
  z-index: 10;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
thead th:first-child { width: 44px; }
tbody tr {
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.1s;
}
tbody tr:hover { background: var(--bg2); }
tbody tr:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--red); outline-offset: -2px; }
tbody tr.is-open { background: #FEF9F0; }
td { padding: 0.7rem 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; }
td:first-child {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  color: var(--muted);
  white-space: nowrap;
  padding-top: 0.85rem;
}
.item-name {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.3;
  margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
}
.item-preview {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.4;
}
.cat-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--cond);
  font-size: 0.63rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 0.18rem 0.5rem;
  border-radius: 3px;
  color: #fff;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.change-val { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.45; }
.effective-val { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.74rem; color: var(--muted); white-space: nowrap; }
.revenue-val { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.74rem; color: var(--gold); }
.revenue-na { color: var(--muted); }
.source-val { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }
.expand-row { display: none; }
.expand-row td {
  background: #FFFDF7;
  padding: 0.9rem 0.9rem 0.9rem 3rem;
  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
}
.expand-row p {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: #4B5563;
  line-height: 1.75;
  max-width: 720px;
}
.expand-row p strong { color: var(--text); }
.expand-icon {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  color: var(--muted);
  transition: transform 0.15s;
  display: inline-block;
  margin-right: 4px;
}
.is-open .expand-icon { transform: rotate(90deg); color: var(--red); }
.no-results {
  text-align: center; padding: 3rem;
  font-family: var(--serif); font-style: italic; color: var(--muted); display: none;
}

/* ===== LOWER ===== */
.lower-sections {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 2rem 1.5rem 3rem;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 2rem;
  align-items: start;
}
.sources-box {
  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  background: var(--bg2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
}
.sources-box h3 {
  font-family: var(--cond);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}
.sources-box p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
.sources-box p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

/* ===== FOOTER ===== */
footer {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  font-family: var(--cond);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  color: var(--muted);
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .masthead-stats { display: none; }
  .lower-sections { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .col-revenue { display: none; }
}
@media (max-width: 680px) {
  .col-effective { display: none; }
  .masthead-inner { grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; }
  .masthead-nav { display: none; }
  td, thead th { padding: 0.55rem 0.5rem; }
  thead th { white-space: normal; }
  thead th:first-child { width: 30px; }
  td:first-child { padding-top: 0.7rem; }
  .expand-row td { padding: 0.8rem 0.75rem 0.8rem 1.5rem; }
  .change-val, .source-val { overflow-wrap: anywhere; }
}
@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .col-change { display: none; }
  .table-wrap { padding: 0 0.75rem 2rem; }
  .filter-bar-inner { padding: 0.55rem 0.75rem; }
  .masthead-inner { padding: 0 0.75rem; }
  .cat-badge { white-space: normal; }
  .lower-sections { padding: 2rem 0.75rem 3rem; }
  footer { padding: 1.25rem 0.75rem; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.25rem; }
}

/* ===== VIEW TOGGLE ===== */
[hidden] { display: none !important; }
.view-toggle {
  background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  font-family: var(--cond); font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); padding: 0; transition: color 0.2s;
}
.view-toggle:hover { color: var(--text); }
.view-toggle.active { color: var(--red); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--red); padding-bottom: 2px; }

/* ===== BY-LEGISLATOR MATRIX ===== */
#view-legislator { --dem:#1D4ED8; --rep:#B91C1C; --ind:#6B7280; --yes-bg:#FCEBE9; --na:#EDEBE8; }
#view-legislator .controls { background: var(--bg2); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); position: sticky; top: var(--masthead-h,62px); z-index: 50; }
#view-legislator .controls-inner { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
#view-legislator .search { flex: 1 1 220px; min-width: 180px; position: relative; }
#view-legislator .search input { width: 100%; font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 0.45rem 0.7rem 0.45rem 1.9rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 20px; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); }
#view-legislator .search input:focus { outline: 2px solid var(--red); outline-offset: -1px; }
#view-legislator .search::before { content: "\2315"; position: absolute; left: 0.65rem; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); color: var(--muted); font-size: 1rem; }
#view-legislator .seg { display: flex; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; font-family: var(--cond); font-size: 0.74rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; }
#view-legislator .seg button { background: var(--bg); color: var(--muted); border: none; padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem; cursor: pointer; border-right: 1px solid var(--border); line-height: 1.5; }
#view-legislator .seg button:last-child { border-right: none; }
#view-legislator .seg button.active { background: var(--red); color: #fff; }
#view-legislator .filter-count { margin-left: auto; }
#view-legislator .filter-count b { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
#view-legislator .matrix-wrap { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 1rem 1.5rem 2rem; }
#view-legislator .scroll { overflow: auto; max-height: 74vh; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); }
#view-legislator table { border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0; font-size: 0.85rem; width: 100%; min-width: 640px; }
#view-legislator thead th { background: var(--bg); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 5; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border); font-family: var(--cond); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); padding: 0.5rem 0.45rem 0.6rem; line-height: 1.25; width: 106px; white-space: normal; }
#view-legislator thead th.bill { border-left: 2px solid var(--border); }
#view-legislator thead th .lbl { display: block; font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.03em; color: var(--text); }
#view-legislator thead th .chap { display: block; font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 1px; }
#view-legislator thead th .tally { display: block; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.62rem; color: var(--text); margin-top: 3px; letter-spacing: 0; text-transform: none; font-weight: 400; }
#view-legislator .name-head { text-align: left; padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem; font-size: 0.66rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em; width: auto; }
#view-legislator th.sticky-col, #view-legislator td.sticky-col { position: sticky; left: 0; background: var(--bg); min-width: 200px; max-width: 240px; border-right: 1px solid var(--border); }
#view-legislator td.sticky-col { z-index: 3; }
#view-legislator thead th.sticky-col { z-index: 7; }
#view-legislator tbody tr { cursor: default; }
#view-legislator tbody tr:hover td { background: var(--bg2); }
#view-legislator td { padding: 0.5rem 0.4rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); white-space: normal; }
#view-legislator .leg-name { font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.2; }
#view-legislator .leg-meta { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.66rem; color: var(--muted); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; margin-top: 2px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
#view-legislator .party { display: inline-block; font-family: var(--cond); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.6rem; min-width: 16px; height: 16px; line-height: 16px; padding: 0 3px; text-align: center; border-radius: 3px; color: #fff; }
#view-legislator .party.D { background: var(--dem); } #view-legislator .party.R { background: var(--rep); } #view-legislator .party.I, #view-legislator .party.U { background: var(--ind); }
#view-legislator .chamber-tag { font-family: var(--cond); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
#view-legislator td.vote { border-left: 1px solid var(--border); }
#view-legislator td.vote.bill { border-left: 2px solid var(--border); }
#view-legislator td.yes { background: var(--yes-bg); }
#view-legislator .x { color: var(--red); font-family: var(--cond); font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1; }
#view-legislator .dot { color: var(--border); font-family: var(--mono); }
#view-legislator .novote { color: var(--muted); font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.78rem; }
#view-legislator td.notseated { background: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, var(--na), var(--na) 4px, transparent 4px, transparent 8px); }
#view-legislator td.score { border-left: 2px solid var(--border); font-family: var(--cond); font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--red); }
#view-legislator td.score .of { color: var(--muted); font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.72rem; }
#view-legislator .divider td { background: var(--bg3); font-family: var(--cond); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); text-align: left; padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem; position: sticky; left: 0; }
#view-legislator .lower { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem 3rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: start; }
#view-legislator .box { padding: 1.1rem 1.35rem; background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); }
#view-legislator .box h3 { font-family: var(--cond); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.7rem; }
#view-legislator .box p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
#view-legislator .key { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
#view-legislator .key-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text); }
#view-legislator .key-swatch { width: 30px; height: 22px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 3px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex: 0 0 auto; }
#view-legislator .src-list { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; }
@media (max-width: 760px) { #view-legislator .lower { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="masthead">
  <div class="masthead-inner">
    <div class="masthead-brand">
      <div class="masthead-count">32</div>
      <div class="masthead-title">Times Augusta Raised Taxes<span>or Fees Since 2019</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="masthead-stats">
      <div class="mstat"><div class="mstat-val">#5</div><div class="mstat-label">Most Taxed State</div></div>
      <div class="mstat"><div class="mstat-val">65%</div><div class="mstat-label">Spending Growth Since 2018</div></div>
      <div class="mstat"><div class="mstat-val">$292M</div><div class="mstat-label">Rainy Day Fund Drained</div></div>
    </div>
    <nav class="masthead-nav" aria-label="Views">
      <button class="view-toggle active" data-view="tax">By Tax</button>
      <button class="view-toggle" data-view="legislator">By Legislator</button>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<div id="view-tax">
<div class="filter-bar">
  <div class="filter-bar-inner">
    <div class="cat-chips" role="group" aria-label="Filter by category">
      <button class="cat-chip active" data-cat="all">All (32)</button>
      <button class="cat-chip" data-cat="consumer">Consumer / Sales</button>
      <button class="cat-chip" data-cat="income">Income Tax</button>
      <button class="cat-chip" data-cat="payroll">Payroll</button>
      <button class="cat-chip" data-cat="business">Business</button>
      <button class="cat-chip" data-cat="healthcare">Healthcare</button>
      <button class="cat-chip" data-cat="fee">Fees &amp; Licenses</button>
      <button class="cat-chip" data-cat="fiscal">Fiscal Policy</button>
    </div>
    <div class="filter-count">Showing <span id="visibleCount">32</span> of <span id="totalCount">32</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<main>
<div class="table-wrap" id="tracker">
  <table id="trackerTable" aria-label="Tax and fee increases under Governor Mills since 2019">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>#</th>
        <th>Increase</th>
        <th>Category</th>
        <th class="col-change">Change</th>
        <th class="col-effective">Effective</th>
        <th class="col-revenue">Revenue Impact</th>
        <th>Legislative Source</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody id="trackerBody"></tbody>
  </table>
  <p class="no-results" id="noResults">No increases match this filter.</p>
</div>

<div class="lower-sections" id="sources">
  <div class="sources-box">
    <h3>Sources &amp; Methodology</h3>
    <p>Entries are compiled from enacted Maine public laws and budget documents: the FY2024&ndash;25 biennial budget (PL 2023, c. 412), the 2024 supplemental budget (PL 2023, c. 643), the FY2026&ndash;27 biennial budget (PL 2025, c. 388), and the 2026 supplemental budget (LD 2212, signed April 10, 2026).</p>
    <p>Revenue figures come from Maine Revenue Services and the Department of Administrative and Financial Services where available, supplemented by estimates from the Maine Policy Institute (MPI) and the Maine Center for Economic Policy (MECEP), and reporting from the Maine Morning Star, Portland Press Herald, Maine Public, The Maine Monitor, and The Maine Wire. The &ldquo;#5 most taxed state&rdquo; figure is WalletHub&rsquo;s 2026 tax-burden ranking.</p>
    <p>Where no official standalone estimate exists, entries are marked &ldquo;Not separately scored.&rdquo;</p>
  </div>
  <div class="sources-box">
    <h3>What Counts as an Increase</h3>
